  "title": "Food Quality Technologist (Manufacturing)",
  "description": "<p>Our client, a leading player in the <strong>Food & Ingredients industry.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a <strong>Food Quality Technologis</strong>t be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects and support R&D projects. They are located in the <strong>West</strong> - easily accessible.<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and apply emulsifiers for cakes, rolls, and pastries.</li><li>Formulate new food improvers and bakery recipes; conduct shelf-life testing.</li><li>Perform baking trials, product evaluations, and comparison tests.</li><li>Provide technical support to internal teams and customers; troubleshoot on-site.</li><li>Collaborate with Sales to ensure products meet client requirements.</li><li>Propose innovative concepts based on market trends and business needs.</li><li>Present products and conduct live demos/seminars.</li><li>Ensure compliance with legislation and maintain hygiene and safety standards.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Food Science or related field.</li><li>Experience in R&D in flour milling, bakery, related ingredient industries</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.<br />EA License No: 19C9682<br />EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</p>",
